data.description: If you are looking for adventure and new discoveries, come take a look at this 4 bedrooms with 3 and half baths home that is surrounded by historic charm. With a TRANSFERABLE BUILDER WARRANTY! Located in Winter Garden, this property gives you access to the historic downtown areas. The location also offers easy commutes to Orlando International Airport and just a 30-minute drive to Disney World. There is so much to explore in this area! If you are into biking, the West Orange Trail is right down the road which allows you to ride your bike to the downtown areas that are close by to go to the local brewery, restaurants and/or shops. This bike trail has over 32 miles to roam. The home has plenty of space to entertain and room for a growing family with 2998 SQFT of living space with a 3-car garage. The Main living area is on the 1st floor along with the Primary Suite located at the back of the home for privacy and offers a getaway from the guest rooms which are on the 2nd floor. The Primary en suite bathroom has a double vanity, walk-in shower, garden tub, toilet room with privacy door as well as a spacious walk-in closet. The 1st floor also offers a flex space that can be used as desired. You can make it an office/study, formal living or use it as a dining area. The Kitchen is well equipped with ample storage and counterspace, even has a dry bar in the hall which would make a great coffee station. Off the kitchen is a dining and family room combo that leads to the screened in lanai. The backyard is not fully fenced. But the surrounding neighbors are, so a small amount of fencing is needed to fully close in the backyard. These properties sit on quarter acre lots so the back yard is quite roomy for future add-ons like a pool. The 2nd floor of the home has the rest of the guest suites with storage closets and multiple full bathrooms. Two of the rooms share a Jack and Jill bath. The 2nd floor also provides a Large Game Room. Home is Connected smart home technology package which allows you to control your home with your smart device while near or away. Come take a tour of this Portland Floor plan that is ready for a quick move in, located in Lake Apopka Sound. Virtual walk through is provided on this listing! Follow the link to tour the property today! https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=uzw9wRafp8T&mls=1
